11-09  Time Conversions (6)
  pg 167, #5.25

converting milliseconds to hours, minutes, and seconds
Write a method that converts milliseconds to hours, minutes, and seconds using
the following header:
  public static String convertMillis(long millis)

The method returns a string `hours:minutes:seconds'. For exampke,
convertMillis(5500) returns a string 0:0:5, convertMillis(100000) returns a
string 0:1:40, and convertMillis(555550000) returns a string 154:19:10
